A '''scalp hunter''' was an occupation held by history teacher [[Kaltor Naklian]] after he resigned from his post at [[University of Timb]].<ref name="AIR">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

Initially Naklian hunted non-sentient creatures to sell their scalps. Noticing his efficiency, he decided to hunt sentient beings too. The goal was selling the scalps; there was a market for [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] scalps among [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]]-wannabees.<ref name="AIR" />

Naklian combined this occupation with his job as [[Third Prophet]] of [[Ni'Shaw-Dak Ministry|Ni'Shaw-Dak]] religion. However, the incomes of scalp hunting were destined to the [[Zulirian Swordmasters]] while the incomes for being Third Prophet were destined to the Religion.<ref name="AIR" />

